text = "Mythic Odyssey is a top-down Action RPG forged 
in the spirit of classic adventure. Master 
precision directional combat, navigate perilous 
environments, and track your triumphs through 
the Hunter’s Ledger. Every victory brings you closer 
to legendary power; every defeat is a lesson in
survival."
